dataprimeQuery.text:
source logs
| filter $d.logger != null
| create size from (byteLength($d:string) + byteLength($l:string) + byteLength($m:string))
| groupby $d.logger agg (sum(size) / 1024 / 1024 / 1024) * 0.6 as price_num
| orderby price_num desc
| limit 100
| create price from concat(round(price_num, 2), ' $')
| choose $d.logger as logger, price

widgets.title: Cost by Logger cost diff by 1w & 1m

dataprimeQuery.text:
source logs
| filter $d.logger != null
| create size from (byteLength($d:string) + byteLength($l:string) + byteLength($m:string))
| groupby $d.logger as logger agg (sum(size) / 1024 / 1024 / 1024) * 0.6 as price_num
| join (
    source logs timeshifted -7d
    | filter $d.logger != null
    | create size_1w from (byteLength($d:string) + byteLength($l:string) + byteLength($m:string))
    | groupby $d.logger as logger agg (sum(size_1w) / 1024 / 1024 / 1024) * 0.6 as price_num_1w
    | create price_1w from concat(round(price_num_1w, 2), ' $')
) on left=>logger == right=>logger into joined_1w
| join (
    source logs timeshifted -30d
    | filter $d.logger != null
    | create size_1m from (byteLength($d:string) + byteLength($l:string) + byteLength($m:string))
    | groupby $d.logger as logger agg (sum(size_1m) / 1024 / 1024 / 1024) * 0.6 as price_num_1m
    | create price_1m from concat(round(price_num_1m, 2), ' $')
) on left=>logger == right=>logger into joined_1m
| create price from concat(round(price_num, 2), ' $')
| orderby price_num desc
| choose logger, price as current_price, joined_1w.price_1w as price_last_week, joined_1m.price_1m as price_last_30d
| limit 50
